_json.description: I have a copper sink in my bathroom and the number one question I get is: Did My Copper Sink Patina? Yes! It did, but it's really easy to clean a copper sink and restore the luster. Click through to learn how to clean a copper sink and read my review about Wright's Copper Cream, a really great copper cleaner that cleans, shines and restores copper. #coppersink Plus you can see more photos of my copper sink bathroom vanity situation!
